# Phase 8: event.stopPropagation()

## Learn Propagation Control

### Understand Purpose

* [ ] Explain why bubbling can be problematic
* [ ] Understand event isolation

### Use stopPropagation

```jsx
function handleClick(event) {
  event.stopPropagation();
}
```

### Practice

