# Phase 11: Controlled Components

## Learn Controlled Inputs

### Understand Single Source of Truth

```jsx
const [name, setName] = useState("");
```

```jsx
<input
  value={name}
  onChange={(e) => setName(e.target.value)}
/>
```

### Learn Benefits

* [ ] Validation
* [ ] Predictability
* [ ] State synchronization

### Practice

* [ ] Build login form
* [ ] Build signup form
* [ ] Build search box

### Milestone

* [ ] Explain why React prefers controlled components

