# Phase 17: Common Mistakes

## Event Handler Mistakes

* [ ] Calling handlers immediately

```jsx
onClick={handleClick()}
```

* [ ] Fix with:

```jsx
onClick={handleClick}
```

or

```jsx
onClick={() => handleClick()}
```

## Form Mistakes

* [ ] Missing preventDefault
* [ ] Uncontrolled state confusion
* [ ] Incorrect input updates

## Propagation Mistakes

* [ ] Unexpected bubbling
* [ ] Incorrect stopPropagation usage

### Milestone

* [ ] Debug event-related bugs quickly

